Happy Hour Finder


Goal of App:

Easy way to find happy hours based on your location.

Features:

Use color coding and ajax requests from google map feature to figure out if there is a bar/restaurant within your area that is currently in happy hour, about to begin happy hour, or about to end happy hour.
Allow user to view menu with a single click.

Reach Feature: Allow restaurant to create "push notification" to people in the area about specials or promos for that day
